@startuml
title Figure 22. Web Voice Job Assistant Sequence Diagram
actor "Browser User" as User
participant "Web Voice UI\n(Next.js + Web Speech API)" as WebUI
participant "NestJS Career Assistant API" as API
participant "Google Gemini API" as Gemini
database "PostgreSQL (Prisma)" as DB
participant "TTS Service" as TTS

User -> WebUI : speak job request
WebUI -> WebUI : speech-to-text
WebUI -> API : POST /career-assistant/chat\n(message, profileSummary, needs)
API -> Gemini : analyze intent + rank response
Gemini --> API : suggested response / reasoning
API -> DB : fetch suitable jobs
DB --> API : matching jobs
API -> TTS : synthesize response audio
TTS --> API : audioUrl / spoken output
API --> WebUI : answer + suggestedJobs + audioUrl
WebUI --> User : spoken feedback + job suggestions

@enduml
